# IS Fleet — Прогрес

## Стек
- Backend: NestJS + TypeScript
- DB: PostgreSQL + Prisma (Supabase)
- Real-time: Socket.io
- Web: Next.js
- Mobile: React Native + Expo
- Files: Cloudinary
- Translate: Google Translate API
- Push: Firebase FCM
- Auth: JWT + Twilio (OTP)
- Email: Nodemailer + Outlook SMTP
- Deploy: Railway + Vercel + Supabase

